Package: sameplot
Title: Consistent plot rendering and saving via ragg and knitr
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Tom", "Naber", , "tomnaber12@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Renders plots to a temporary image using ragg and returns a knitr include with the option to save the image to a specified path,
    ensuring consistent appearance across interactive sessions, saved files, and knitted documents.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports:
    knitr,
    ragg
Suggests: 
    ggplot2,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/TomNaber/sameplot
BugReports: https://github.com/TomNaber/sameplot/issues
